		<li>PostgreSQL 7.3+</li>
		<li>SQLite 2.8.2+</li>
		<li>Firebird 2.1+</li>
		<li>MS SQL Server 2000 or above (directly or via ODBC)</li>
		<li>MS SQL Server 2005 or above (native)</li>
		<li>Oracle</li>
	</ul>

